OL,3,CSidecar racing brothers 'feel lucky'
OL,4,Cto be alive after 160mph TT crash
OL,6,FA few weeks ago, riders were taking on
OL,7,Fthe twists and turns of the Mountain
OL,8,FCourse at the Isle of Man TT races,
OL,9,Fbut for two Manx sidecar brothers,
OL,10,Ftheir racing fortnight ended in
OL,11,Fhospital.
OL,13,FRyan and Callum Crowe were involved in
OL,14,Fa 160-mile-an-hour crash during a
OL,15,Fqualifying session.
OL,17,FOn the approach to an elevated section
OL,18,Fof the course, their sidecar flipped
OL,19,Finto the air - an incident so serious,
OL,20,Fit led to the suspension of the whole
OL,21,FSidecar class for this year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
