FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782389902
OL,3,CSidecar racing brothers 'feel lucky'
OL,4,Cto be alive after 160mph TT crash
OL,6,FNow out of hospital, the four-time
OL,7,FIsle of Man TT sidecar race winners
OL,8,Fhave been reflecting on the incident.
OL,10,FSidecar driver Ryan Crowe said: "I
OL,11,Fremember it going up and seeing the
OL,12,Fsky, and then I also remember it
OL,13,Fcoming down, landing on me upside
OL,14,Fdown, down the road, and then I
OL,15,Fremember waking up and talking to him
OL,16,Fat the side of the road."
OL,18,FSidecar passenger Callum said: "You
OL,19,Fknow, we had some serious people
OL,20,Flooking down at us on that day, and we
OL,21,Fare very, very lucky.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782389902
OL,3,CSidecar racing brothers 'feel lucky'
OL,4,Cto be alive after 160mph TT crash
OL,6,F"We race at the Isle of Man TT and we
OL,7,Fall know the risks, and we just hit
OL,8,Fone of those risks."
OL,10,FWhile the brothers were lucky to
OL,11,Fescape with their lives, concern grew
OL,12,Ffor the safety of side cars, leading
OL,13,Fto the immediate suspension of the
OL,14,Fclass and an investigation launched.
OL,16,F"Yeah, I can kind of understand why
OL,17,Fthey... why they've pulled it out and
OL,18,Funder review", Ryan said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782389902
OL,3,CSidecar racing brothers 'feel lucky'
OL,4,Cto be alive after 160mph TT crash
OL,6,F"Obviously, when something like that
OL,7,Fhappens out on a track of spectators
OL,8,Fall stood around you've got to take a
OL,9,Fserious review into the safety of not
OL,10,Fonly riders, but you've got the
OL,11,Fmedics, the marshals, the spectators
OL,12,Fand the general public."
OL,14,FCallum adds: "It's the Isle of Man TT
OL,15,Forganisers' decision, and, well, you
OL,16,Fcan't argue with them."
OL,18,F"At the end of the day, they're
OL,19,Fofficials, they run the show, and they
OL,20,Fdon't think we're safe that's up to
OL,21,Fthem."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,367,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F366A1782389902
OL,3,CSidecar racing brothers 'feel lucky'
OL,4,Cto be alive after 160mph TT crash
OL,6,FDespite the brother's injuries, it
OL,7,Fhasn't deterred them from racing the
OL,8,Froads.
OL,10,FCallum said: "If my body allowed me to
OL,11,Fgo out on that bike the next day, and
OL,12,FI was fit, I'd be back out on that
OL,13,Fbike the next day."
OL,15,FThe brothers say their bike is being
OL,16,Frepaired, and they hope to get back on
OL,17,Fit later this year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
